Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE Hotels & Ray White Hotels are pleased to offer for sale the iconic resort in the heart of Terrigal, NSW.

- Beachfront resort with extensive business and leisure facilities on a 9,336m2 freehold parcel of land
- 199 well-appointed guest rooms and suites with an average room size of 39m2
- Popular conferencing and weekend destination on the Central Coast (90 minutes from Sydney)
- Multiple revenue streams: conferencing, food & beverage, accommodation, 21 gaming machine entitlements, 20 retail tenancies
- Resort presents immaculately after undergoing $10.6 million in refurbishments between 2010-2014
- Operated by the world renowned InterContinental Hotels Group (IHG)

FOR SALE BY WAY OF A PUBLIC INTERNATIONAL EXPRESSION OF INTEREST CAMPAIGN CLOSING (IF NOT SOLD PRIOR)
